#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Cilj:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go through the levels by eating all pills and energizers."
msgstr "Pojdite skozi ravni tako, da pojeste vse tablete in vire energije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kapman; will load level one once you start the game. To start the game, "
"press an arrow key. You move straight ahead without pressing any key. To "
"turn, press an arrow key. You should not turn at the last moment, but "
"anticipate and you will turn as soon as possible. To eat a pill, an "
"energizer, a bonus, or even a ghost, you must get in touch with it. When all "
"the pills and energizers have been eaten, you move to the next level."
msgstr ""
"&kapman; bo naložil prvo raven, ko začnete igro. Za začetek igre pritisnite "
"puščično tipko. Pomikate se naravnost naprej, ne da bi pritisnili katero "
"koli tipko. Za obračanje pritisnite puščično tipko. Ne smete se obrniti "
"zadnji trenutek, ampak predvidevajte in se obrnite čim prej. Če želite "
"pojesti tableto, vir energije, bonus ali celo duha, morate priti v stik z "
"njim. Ko pojeste vse tablete in vire energije, se pomaknete na naslednjo "
"raven."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila igre, strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To move to the next level, you must eat every pill and energizer in the maze."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preiti na naslednjo stopnjo, morate pojesti vsako tableto in vir "
"energije v labirintu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A bonus appears when you have eaten 1/3 and 2/3 of the pills and energizers. "
"It disappears after a few seconds (10 seconds at the first level, but it "
"decreases as the level increases) if you have not eaten it."
msgstr ""
"Bonus se prikaže, ko pojeste 1/3 in 2/3 tablet in virov energije. Bonus "
"izgine po nekaj sekundah (10 sekund na prvi stopnji, vendar se zmanjšuje, ko "
"se raven zvišuje), če ga niste pojedli."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the level increases, both your speed and the ghosts speed increase. "
"However, the ghosts will be more and more faster than you."
msgstr ""
"Z višanjem ravni se povečata tako vaša hitrost kot hitrost duhov. Vendar pa "
"bodo duhovi vedno hitrejši od vas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you get in touch with a ghost, you lose a life, and the current level "
"restarts (but the eaten pills and energizer do not reappear)."
msgstr ""
"Če pridete v stik z duhom, izgubite življenje in trenutna raven se znova "
"zažene (vendar se pojedene tablete in viri energije ne pojavijo znova)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are in the line of sight of a ghost (that is to say : no wall between "
"the ghost, and both of you go to the same direction), the ghost will hunt "
"you. Otherwise, the ghosts have a random moving."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v vidnem polju duha (to pomeni: med duhom ni zidu in gresta oba v "
"isto smer), vas bo duh lovil. V nasprotnem primeru se duhovi premikajo "
"naključno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you eat an energizer, the ghosts slow down and you can eat them. If you "
"eat a ghost, it goes back to its home and its normal behaviour. After a few "
"seconds (10 seconds at the first level, but it decreases as the level "
"increases), the ghosts that have not been eaten go back to their normal "
"behaviour."
msgstr ""
"Ko pojeste vir energije, se duhovi upočasnijo in jih lahko pojeste. Če "
"pojeste duha, se vrne v svoj dom in se normalno vede. Po nekaj sekundah (10 "
"sekund na prvi stopnji, vendar se zmanjšuje, ko se raven zvišuje), se "
"duhovi, ki niso bili pojedeni, vrnejo k običajnemu vedenju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "You win points when eating an item:"
msgstr "Točke osvojite, ko pojeste izdelek:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Item values"
msgstr "Vrednosti predmetov"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pill"
msgstr "Tabletka"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "10 points"
msgstr "10 točk"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Energizer"
msgstr "Vir energije"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "20 points"
msgstr "20 točk"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus"
msgstr "Bonus"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current level * 100 points"
msgstr "Trenutna raven * 100 točk"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ghost"
msgstr "Duh"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It depends on the number of ghosts you have eaten since the last energizer "
"was eaten:"
msgstr ""
"Odvisno je od števila duhov, ki ste jih pojedli od zadnjega zaužitja vira "
"energije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "1st ghost: 100 points"
msgstr "1. duh: 100 točk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "2nd ghost: 200 points"
msgstr "2. duh: 200 točk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "3rd ghost: 400 points"
msgstr "3. duh: 400 točk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "4th ghost: 800 points"
msgstr "4. duh: 800 točk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "You get a life more every 10,000 points you win."
msgstr "Za vsakih 10.000 osvojenih točk dobite življenje več."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije in nasveti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To eat an item, you must get it touch with its center, not only a few "
"pixels. So be sure you have really eaten what you wanted, before turning "
"back."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pojesti predmet, se ga morate dotakniti s središčem, ne le z nekaj "
"slikovnimi pikami. Zato se prepričajte, da ste res pojedli, kar ste želeli, "
"preden se obrnete nazaj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At first levels, the bonus does not make a lot of points and ghosts are not "
"very fast, so you should concentrate on eating the most ghosts that you can."
msgstr ""
"Na prvih stopnjah bonus ne prinaša veliko točk in duhovi niso zelo hitri, "
"zato se morate osredotočiti na to, da pojeste čim več duhov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After about ten levels, the ghosts are faster and the bonus makes more "
"points, so you should try to eat the bonus when possible. Do not hesitate to "
"eat an energizer when you can see the bonus, to not be disturbed by the "
"ghosts."
msgstr ""
"Po približno desetih stopnjah so duhovi hitrejši in bonus prinaša več točk, "
"zato poskusite pojesti bonus, ko je to mogoče. Ne oklevajte in pojejte vir "
"energije, ko boste videli bonus, da vas ne bodo motili duhovi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the same way, you should try to eat an energizer before going to the "
"dangerous places (like near the ghost home)."
msgstr ""
"Na enak način bi morali poskusiti pojesti vir energije, preden greste na "
"nevarna mesta (na primer blizu doma duhov)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the ghosts are too fast, you should avoid to eat them if you are near "
"their home. They could go back faster than you think."
msgstr ""
"Ko so duhovi prehitri, se jim izogibajte, če ste blizu njihovega doma. Lahko "
"bi se vrnili hitreje, kot si mislite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not hesitate to stay in the same place for a few seconds, waiting for the "
"ghosts to go far away from the place you need to go."
msgstr ""
"Ne oklevajte in ostanite na istem mestu nekaj sekund in počakajte, da duhovi "
"odidejo daleč stran od mesta, kamor morate iti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find cheatcodes from the source code. But be careful: if you make a "
"new high score but have cheated, your high score will not be registered."
msgstr ""
"Kode goljufij najdete v izvorni kodi. Vendar bodite previdni: če dosežete "
"novo visoko oceno, vendar ste goljufali, vaša visoka ocena ne bo zabeležena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last but not least: Have fun !"
msgstr "Nenazadnje: zabavajte se!"

