msgstr "<guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremeni raven</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Brings up the level selection dialog. Be careful: changing the current level "
"will make the game consider you as a cheater, so you will not able to "
"register in the high scores table."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogovorno okno za izbiro ravni. Bodite previdni: če spremenite "
"trenutno raven, vas bo igra obravnavala kot goljufa, zato se ne boste mogli "
"prijaviti v tabelo z najboljšimi rezultati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Game</guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Quits</action> &kapman;."
msgstr "<action>Zapusti</action> &kapman;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Predvajaj zvoke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plays the sounds or mutes."
msgstr "Predvaja ali utiša zvoke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu>Težavnost</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjusts the game difficulty to <guimenuitem>Easy</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodi težavnost igre na <guimenuitem>Enostavno</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Srednje</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Težko</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kapman; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
"<guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the sections "
"about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega &kapman; ima skupno &kde; Elementi menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij preberite razdelke o "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">meniju z "
"nastavitvami</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-help"
"\">meni Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnove."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default Keybindings"
msgstr "Privzete vezave tipk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Turn up</action> - &Up; arrow"
msgstr "<action>Obrni gor</action> -  &Up; puščica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Turn down</action> - &Down; arrow"
msgstr "<action>Obrni dol</action> – &Down; puščica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Turn right</action> - &Right; arrow"
msgstr "<action>Obrni desno</action> - &Right; puščica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Turn left</action> - &Left; arrow"
msgstr "<action>Obrni levo</action> - &Left; puščica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Pause</action> - <keycap>P</keycap> or &Esc;"
msgstr "<action>Pavza</action> - <keycap>P</keycap> ali &Esc;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Vprašanja in odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Želim spremeniti videz te igre. Ali lahko?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the &kapman; theme in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kapman;…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. "
"See the <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</link> chapter "
"for more details."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko &kapman; temo v pogovornem oknu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kapman;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Za več podrobnosti glejte poglavje "
"<link linkend=\"configuration\">Konfiguracija igre</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I skip a level?"
msgstr "Ali lahko preskočim nivo?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to change the current level. In both cases, you will be "
"considered as a cheater and you will not be able to register to the high "
"scores. The first way is using a cheatcode. I let you find it. The other way "
"is selecting the level you want from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Game</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Change Level</guimenuitem></menuchoice> dialog. See the "
"<link linkend=\"menu\">Menubar</link> section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno raven lahko spremenite na dva načina. V obeh primerih vas bodo "
"obravnavali kot goljufa in se ne boste mogli prijaviti na visoke rezultate. "
"Prvi način je uporaba goljufive kode. Pustil sem ti, da ga najdeš. Drugi "
"način je, da izberete želeno raven v pogovornem oknu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Igra</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spremeni raven</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"menu\">Menijska vrstica</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change default keyboard shortcuts?"
msgstr "Ali lahko spremenim privzete bližnjice na tipkovnici?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is not possible for now. But will be a new feature in a future version of "
"&kapman;. See the <link linkend=\"keybindings\">Default Keybindings</link> "
"section for more details."
msgstr ""
"Za zdaj ni mogoče. Toda to bo nova funkcija v prihodnji različici &kapman;. "
"Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"keybindings\">Privzete "
"vezave tipk</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Zdaj moram zapustiti igro, vendar še nisem končal. Ali lahko shranim svoj "
"napredek?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can not, and it is deliberate. We think that the game would be too easy "
"if you could save the game and reload it as you lose your lives."
msgstr ""
"Ne morete in to je namerno. Menimo, da bi bila igra prelahka, če bi jo lahko "
"shranili in jo znova naložili, ko izgubite življenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I get more lives?"
msgstr "Kako lahko dobim več življenj?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two ways to get lives. The first one is using a cheatcode. I let "
"you find it. The other way is winning points. Every 10,000 points, you get a "
"life more. See the <link linkend=\"rules\">Rules</link> section for more "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Obstajata dva načina za pridobitev življenj. Prvi je uporaba kode goljufije. "
"Pustili smo, da ga najdete. Drugi način je osvajanje točk. Vsakih 10.000 "
"točk dobite življenje več. Za več podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend="
"\"rules\">Pravila</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija igre"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the theme you want to play &kapman;. To do that, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kapman;…</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The &kapman; configuration dialog (see below) "
"appears and you can then select the theme. It is immediately changed on "
"validating your choice, no need to restart the game. You can click on the "
"<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> button to restore the default theme."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko temo, ki jo želite igrati &kapman;. Če želite to narediti, "
"izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kapman;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. &kapman; prikaže se konfiguracijsko "
"pogovorno okno (glejte spodaj), nato pa lahko izberete temo. Takoj se "
"spremeni, ko potrdite svojo izbiro, igre ni treba znova zagnati. Lahko "
"kliknete gumb <guibutton>Privzeto</guibutton>, da obnovite privzeto temo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kapman; configuration dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kapman; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &kapman; configuration dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kapman; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</phrase>"

